properties.areaDesc: Los Angeles County Mountains excluding the Santa Monica Range
properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued February 4 at 9:01AM PST until February 5 at 9:00AM PST by NWS Los Angeles/Oxnard CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northeast winds 25 to 35 mph with gusts up to 50 mph
expected.

* WHERE...Los Angeles County Mountains excluding the Santa
Monica Range.

* WHEN...Until 9 AM PST Wednesday.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds will blow around unsecured objects and
make driving difficult, especially for high profile vehicles.
Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may
result.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 9 AM PST WEDNESDAY
